## Architecture: What We Are Building

One login → one gate-issued session token → accepted by every 0s app.

```
User → 0s Login Page → 0megaSkyeGate /v1/auth/login
                              ↓
                     Gate verifies identity
                     Gate issues signed session JWT
                              ↓
              Session token in localStorage + secure cookie
                              ↓
     Every 0s app reads token → sends as Bearer to gate
                              ↓
           Gate returns user identity + wallet + role
```

Founder bypass unchanged: `x-founders-gateway-key` header = instant sovereign access, skips login page entirely.

